Fate Tola Geleto (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1987) bụ onye Etiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke na-asọ mpi na asọmpi marathon
Ọ nọchitere anya Ethiopia na IAAF World Half Marathon Championships ma merie marathon na Thessaloniki na Vienna
Ọ bi na mba Germany ma soro Irina Mikitenko na-ọzụzụ̀. Kemgbe afọ 2012, ọ na-asọmpi nye klọb German MTV Braunschweig

Otu n'ime ihe ndị mbụ ọ pụtara bụ Great Ethiopian Run n'onwa Nọvemba 2008, ebe ọ gbara nke anọ n'azụ Teyba Erkesso n'elu kilomita iri. O mere mpụtara nke mbụ ya na Alexander the Great Marathon n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2009 ma merie na mgbalị mbụ ya, na-ewere aha otutu ụmụ nwanyị n'ime awa 2:36:54. Ljubljana Marathon n'ọnwa Ọktoba bụ nke abụọ ọ gara n'ihu n'ebe ahụ ma ọ bụ nke anọ, mana ọ meziwanyere oge kachasị mma ya site na nkeji na ọkara.
Ọ nọchitere anya ndị uwe ojii Oromia na Sululta Cross Country na mbido afọ 2010 wee gbaa onye nke anọ
Ọ kwalitere marathon ya nke ọma na Marathon Rome nke afọ ahụ, were nkeji ise n'ime elekere 2:28:54,  wee merie Paderborner Osterlauf 10K n'oge na-adịghị anya
A họpụtara ya ka ọ nọchite anya Etiopia na 2010 IAAF World Half Marathon Championship na Nanning na Ọktọba wee bịa na nke asaa, na-esetịpụ ihe kacha mma nke awa 1:09:38  maka idi anya ya

Ọsọ ikpeazụ  ya kacha n'afọ ahụ bịara na Marathon Turin wee mekwaa ọzọ: ọ ghọrọ asọmpi nwanyị abụọ n'etiti Tola na Priscah Jeptoo na agbanyeghị na ọ bụ onye Kenya na-ama ya aka na-ekwenye na mmeri, Tola gbara ọsọ nke 2:28:22 kacha mma
awa dị ka onye na-agba ọsọ

Oge afọ 2011 ya malitere site na njedebe nke abụọ na Berlin Half Marathon Nke a bụ nkwadebe ya maka Vienna City Marathon na n'ọsọ ahụ ọ meriri ndị mbido Peninah Arusei na Ana Dulce Felix iji merie na nke anọ n'usoro nke elekere 2:26:21 Usoro a bịara na njedebe na Ọktoba Frankfurt Marathon ka oge ya nke awa 2:27:18 wetara ya ọnọdụ nke asaa. Ọ gbachitere aha ya na Vienna Marathon n'afọ 2012 wee bịaruo nso na nke kachasị mma ya na ọsọ nke 2:26:39 awa. Ọnọdụ nke ise na 2012 Berlin Marathon hụrụ ka ọ meziwanye oge ahụ ruo awa2:25:14
